      <h1>Privacy Policy for Cronolaris - Elapse Watchfaces</h1>
    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share information in relation to your use of Cronolaris - Elapse Watchfaces (the "App"). Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>1. Collection of Information</h2>
    <p>The App may collect the following types of information for the sole purpose of displaying relevant data on your watchface:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Fitness Data:</strong> The App may access and display data related to the number of steps taken. This data is only displayed on the watchface and is not transmitted or stored externally.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
    <p>We do not collect, store, or transmit any of the data mentioned above. The data is solely used for the purpose of presenting it on the watchface, and no other use is made of this information.</p>

    <h2>3. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any such changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>4. Contact Information</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at elapsefaces@gmail.com.</p>

    <p>By using the App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>

    <p>Last updated: 03 aug 2024</p>
